Class PaAttributeValueAttributeRequestBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.PaAttributeValueAttributeRequestBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>, PaAttributeValueAttributeRequestBuilder

    public class PaAttributeValueAttributeRequestBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaAttributeValueAttributeRequestBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement attribute request attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
